name: Amjad C P
bio: Solutions Architect at YE Stack | Web-app Pentester | Mentor | DevOps Expert

learn-devops.summary: The 'learn-devops' repository saw recent updates in the form of test implementations, requirement updates, and chore tasks. Key developments include the integration of Selenium tests, updates to the 'requirement.txt' file, and the addition of testing scripts for version v0.1 and v0.2. These updates reflect ongoing efforts in DevOps processes and tooling within this repository.

web2-vs-web3.summary: In 'web2-vs-web3', recent improvements centered on further development and integration of web3 functionality. Key updates encompass the creation of a 'README.md' file, inclusion of an '.env.example' file, and integration of 'getResult' logic into the contract. These updates signal a progression towards utilizing web3 capabilities within this repository.

person-detection-using-cnn-detector.summary: In 'person-detection-using-cnn-detector', significant updates recently took place with the integration of new CNN detection models, featuring the addition of 'Faster R-CNN' and 'RetinaNet'. These integrations aim to enhance the person detection capabilities within this repository.

voting-app.summary: The 'voting-app' repository recently underwent improvements with fixes aimed at addressing issues related to multiple submissions. Additional updates included configuration adjustments to the application port, showcasing efforts to refine the overall functionality of the voting app.

profile_summary:
Amjad C P is a seasoned Solutions Architect and DevOps expert with a strong presence in the developer community, boasting 42 followers and 74 public repositories that demonstrate his active and innovative approach to software development. As a proficient programmer in Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript, he brings a unique combination of technical skills to his role at YE Stack, enabling him to design and implement efficient, scalable solutions that drive business growth.

With a dual expertise in web application penetration testing and DevOps, Amjad provides a holistic approach to software development, prioritizing security, reliability, and performance. As a mentor, he is dedicated to sharing his knowledge and expertise with others, showcasing his passion for collaboration and community building. With a strong track record of delivering high-quality solutions and driving technical innovation, Amjad is a trusted and respected figure in the developer community, known for his technical prowess, problem-solving skills, and dedication to excellence.
